Red & White Holdings Ltd., a
company controlled by Russian billionaire  Alisher Usmanov ,
increased its stake in Arsenal  soccer club .  Red & White said today in a Regulatory News Service
statement that it holds more than 27 percent of the London team.
Usmanov had controlled 26.29 percent of the 13-time English
champion last year, compared with a 29.98 percent stake owned by
U.S. billionaire Stan Kroenke.  To contact the reporter on this story:
